# Image Classification — CIFAR-10 (Week 2 Assignment)

Compares SVM, Softmax, and a Two-layer Neural Network on a 3-class subset of CIFAR-10.

## How to Run

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python image_classification.py
```

## Output Files
| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `sample_images.png` | Grid of sample dataset images |
| `accuracy_comparison.png` | Bar chart comparing all 3 models |
| `confusion_matrix.png` | Confusion matrix for the Neural Network |
| `results_summary.csv` | Accuracy table for all models |